(826, 166, 5, 5, 'a:31:{s:2:"id";s:1:"5";s:3:"sku";s:13:"130-0400-2751";s:4:"name";s:40:"Respond C5 Single Lumen Oxygen Conserver";s:4:"slug";s:41:"respond-c5-single-lumen-oxygen-conserver1";s:8:"route_id";s:1:"5";s:11:"description";s:361:"<ul><li>Whisper quiet - ideal for church, movie bingo outings</li><li>2-in-1 design with built in regulator</li><li>5:1 Conservation {1, 2, 2.5, 3, 4, 5}</li><li>Continuous Flow 2, 3, 4 LPM</li><li>Lightweight - only 12.9 oz</li><li>3 Year warranty</li></ul><p><em><strong>Conserver ships with engraved AeroCare logo unless otherwise selected.</strong></em></p>";s:7:"excerpt";s:0:"";s:5:"price";s:6:"105.00";s:9:"saleprice";s:6:"105.00";s:13:"free_shipping";s:1:"0";s:9:"shippable";s:1:"1";s:7:"taxable";s:1:"1";s:14:"fixed_quantity";s:1:"0";s:6:"weight";s:1:"0";s:11:"track_stock";s:1:"0";s:16:"related_products";s:0:"";s:6:"images";s:110:"{"c3a231f35ac8bd6a9170f14f901b9676":{"filename":"c3a231f35ac8bd6a9170f14f901b9676.jpg","alt":"","caption":""}}";s:9:"seo_title";s:40:"Respond C5 Single Lumen Oxygen Conserver";s:4:"meta";s:57:"Oxygen Conserver - Single Lumen design for medical oxygen";s:7:"enabled";s:1:"1";s:4:"faqs";s:1279:"<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><br>How long will my cylinder last? </strong><br>Please reference the O2 To Go Cylinder Duration Calculator</p><p><strong>What’s the difference between a single and dual lumen conserver?</strong> <br>Dual lumen conservers utilize a special dual tube cannula that senses on one side and delivers oxygen through the other.<br>Dual lumen conservers utilize a special cannula that senses on one side and delivers oxygen through the other tube. Dual lumen conservers are optimal for shallow breathers or those who require a more senstiive device to trigger the oxygen. </p><p><strong>What length of cannula is recommended for use with a Respond C5?</strong><br>RRI recommends a 4’ cannula to maximize sensitivity.</p><p><strong>What’s the difference between a regulator and a conserver?</st