(12, 0, 'Privacy Policy', 'Privacy Policy', 'privacy-policy', 465, '<p class="whitebox"></p><p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 20px;"><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: #3185cb;">Privacy Policy</span></p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">This is the web site of:</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;"><strong>Responsive Respiratory, Inc</strong>.<br>261 Wolfner Drive<br>St. Louis, Mo 63026</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">We can be reached via e-mail at: <a href="mailto:sales@respondo2.com">sales@respondo2.com</a> or by telephone at 866-333-4030.<br> <br>For each visitor to our Web page, our Web server automatically recognizes no information regarding the domain or e-mail address. We do collect aggregate information on what pages consumers'' access or visit, information volunteered by the consumer, such as survey information and/or site registrations, name and address, telephone number, fax number, payment information (e.g., credit card number and billing address). The information we collect is used for internal review and is then discarded. We use cookies to record session information, such as items that consumers add to their shopping cart, record past activity at a site in order to provide better service when visitors return to our site. We have appropriate security measures in place in our physical facilities to protect against the loss, misuse or alteration of information that we have collected from you at our site.</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">If you supply us with your telephone number, postal or email address on-line you may receive periodic communications from us with information regarding orders that have been placed online or on new products and services or upcoming events. If you do not wish to receive such communications, please let us know by calling us at the number provided above or e-mailing or writing to us at the above address. We will be sure your name is removed from the list. We respect your privacy and do not share our lists with any other organizations.</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">Upon request, we provide site visitors with access to unique identifier information (e.g., customer number or password), transaction information (e.g., dates on which customers made purchases, amounts and types of purchases), contact information (e.g., name, address, phone number) that we maintain about them. Consumers can access this information by e-mailing or contacting us at the above address.</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">All materials contained on this site are subject to ownership rights of Responsive Respiratory. Responsive Respiratory hereby authorizes you to copy the content herein for use in learning about, evaluating, purchasing or selling Responsive Respiratory products. Except where noted, no other permission is granted to copy, print, distribute, reproduce, transmit, upload, download, store, alter or modify the content contained on the site. This site contains hypertext links to sites not created or maintained by Responsive Respiratory and Responsive Respiratory is not responsible for the accuracy, completeness, or relevancy of those sites. The inclusion of any link does not imply endorsement, sponsorship or recommendation by Responsive Respiratory of those sites.</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">If you feel that this site is not following its stated information policy, you may contact us at the above addresses or phone number.</p>', 0, '', '', '', 0),
(14, 0, 'Return Policy', 'Return Policy', 'return-policy', 467, '<p class="whitebox" >\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 20px;">\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: #3185cb;">Return Policy</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 20px;">\r\n	<strong>RETURN POLICY:</strong>  If you find it necessary to return an item, please contact our Customer Service Department at (866) 333-4030 and request a Returned Goods Authorization (RGA) number.  The item must be in its original packaging with the original packing slip included.  Used items and products packaged for oxygen use (i.e. conservers, regulators, oxygen disposables) that have been removed from the original packaging (polybag) are not eligible for return.  The RGA number must be clearly marked on the outside of the shipping box.   No packages will be accepted without an RGA number.  Product is eligible to be returned for credit if the return is received by RRI within 30 days of invoice.  Special order and customized items are not eligible for return.  Refunds will only be applied to the original credit card used in the original transaction.  No checks will be issued.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 20px;">\r\n	Return shipping costs are the responsibility of the purchaser – all goods must be sent freight prepaid.  To make a claim on defects in materials and workmanship, Purchaser must notify Responsive Respiratory within 5 days of receipt of the product\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 20px;">\r\n	***\r\n	<span style="text-decoration: underline;">If the product is not in its original packaging or has been damaged, no credit will be issued</span>.  A restocking fee applies to all returns.\r\n</p>', 0, '', '', '', 0),
